column16: Tuffy Gosewisch strikes out on a foul tip.
Cliff Pennington singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Roger Bernadina.   Gerardo Parra to 3rd.    Trevor Cahill to 2nd.
Trevor Cahill singles on a line drive to left fielder Darin Ruf.   Didi Gregorius scores.    Gerardo Parra to 2nd.
